<h2 class="bold font-l">Sylvia reveals their gender</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Kazuma mistakenly thought Sylvia was just a female. They reveal they're actually a hermaphrodite, much to Kazuma's shock. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/UnsettlingGenderReveal" class='trope-example-link'>Unsettling Gender Reveal</a></p>
</div>
